name: Paper Doll Coloring Book
description: Color and customize your own paper dolls!  This coloring book contains six paper dolls total and 29 outfits.  Printed on quality 80 lb card stock paper.  The idea is to either color directly on the pages or make a copy or tracing of the outfit you'd like and do as many versions as you can imagine (there is also be a printable PDF version available).  Either way, the book should give you or your child hours and hours of imaginative play and fun!  This is a book I would have loved as a child so I tried to think of all of the details that would make it special.
